e\": 0.9134376, \"raw_content\": null}, {\"title\": \"The Llama 4 herd: The beginning of a new era of natively ...\", \"url\": \"https://ai.meta.com/blog/llama-4-multimodal-intelligence/\", \"content\": \"* Llama 4 Scout, a 17 billion active parameter model with 16 experts, is the best multimodal model in the world in its class and is more powerful than all previous generation Llama models, while fitting in a single NVIDIA H100 GPU. * Llama 4 Maverick, a 17 billion active parameter model with 128 experts, is the best multimodal model in its class, beating GPT-4o and Gemini 2.0 Flash across a broad range of widely reported benchmarks, while achieving comparable results to the new DeepSeek v3 on reasoning and coding\\u2014at less than half the active parameters. We\\u2019re introducing Llama 4 Scout and Llama 4 Maverick, the first open-weight natively multimodal models with unprecedented context length support and our first built using a mixture-of-experts (MoE) architecture.\", \"score\": 0.91156644, \"raw_content\": null}, {\"title\": \"Llama (language model)\", \"url\": \"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Llama_(language_model)\", \"content\": \"Llama 4 \\u00b7 Scout: 17 billion active parameter model with 16 experts , context window of 10M, with 109B parameters in total. \\u00b7 Maverick: 17 billion active parameter\", \"score\": 0.89166987, \"raw_content\": null}]}"
